## Useful Commands
```bash
# Check deployment status
dockerpilot container list

# Monitor application
dockerpilot monitor myapp --duration 300

# View deployment history
dockerpilot deploy history

# Emergency rollback
dockerpilot deploy config rollback-config.yml --type blue-green
```

